author: Sam Spencer
text: Even with today‚Äôs loss to Union, #RBLeipzig also controls their own destiny as well. Their last two opponents have not escaped relegation so if Augsburg or Arminia decide to fight for their lives, Leipzig could miss Champions League play. #Bundesliga

author: Sam Spencer
text: 3-7 is where it gets interesting in the sprint for international play. Leverkusen is in 3rd but they arguably have the toughest schedule ahead of them with 9th Place Frankfurt, Hoffenheim in 8th, and Freiburg in 5th. They still control their own destiny. #Bundesliga
